name: Jazii - Intuition Remix (LIVE) ft. Cam Murdoch

metadata.description:
Intuition Remix ft. Cam Murdoch offers dual perspectives and gives an entirely new dynamic to the conversation of trusting yourself and that inner voice.

It's my favorite collab thus far, and the live version elevates the vibes  in the best way.

Live instrumentation was done by an extremely talented array of musicians:

Arty J. -Piano, Drums, Synth Bass and Live Arrangement
Cory Kenji- Bass
Patrick Rector-Guitar

Original production by: The Collective
Mix/Master by Joshua "Tipz" Richardson
Vocal Arrangement/Lyrics by Jazzi Richardson
